            "draft_value": "* House Support: Representatives Don Bacon (R-NE) and Judy Chu (D-CA) have led programmatic support letters for this account.\n* Allied Organizations: American Astronomical Society (AAS) and the American Geophysical Union (AGU).\n* Scientific Community: The Planetary Society and its members nationwide support robust funding for the Science Mission Directorate.",
